The abandoned Sealed Route has been compromised by Synod occupation forces who are using the old quarantine corridors to move relic-hazard material past the active Reach inspection network. Whisper Cell commandant leadership, quarantine breach horrors released from containment as tactical cover, and tunnel sentries controlling access must all be eliminated before the Sealed Route can be re-secured. Engage one of each to break the occupation.
The Synod occupation of the Sealed Route has been dismantled. The quarantine breach horrors have been neutralized, the tunnel sentry network is cleared, and the Whisper Cell commandant directorate has been eliminated. The Reach Warden officer has initiated formal re-quarantine procedures on the sealed corridors and filed a relic-hazard incident report with the Khar'Daan funerary authority.

